{"tid":2173814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣將於法國普羅旺斯設立官方辦事處","createTime":"2020-08-25T12:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T12:50:33.000Z","uid":53844,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"437d2d88e19de8a883a9e5c5a15a88fb9bd46220","tid":2173814,"uid":53844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"台灣外交再突破！<br />\n<br />\n台外交部與法國協商討論後，將在南法觀光重鎮普羅旺斯艾克斯（Aix-en-Provence）新設辦事處，促進兩國家的觀光、交流，亦有利於台灣將外交服務深入南法。<br />\n<br />\n這是今年以來，繼台灣駐索馬利蘭代表處落成、駐<br />\n關島辦事處復設後，外交部增設的第三處外館。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-08-25/455597\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-08-25%2F455597&d=byei43Pfdy9TlHy68xWwXTv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=8d3a8dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-08-25/455597</a>"},{"pid":"7e79e644cfca016eef9a703007f7be56223904ba","tid":2173814,"uid":33556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab49325c54a35727c69b4d9dc8c64ddc612eeb64","tid":2173814,"uid":67208,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:02:22.000Z","msg":"一個駐索馬里蘭<br />\n一個駐法國<br />\n<br />\n心理會唔平衡"},{"pid":"d9927ea520cd37c780e5dd5b54df5c3388cdf91b","tid":2173814,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a0b9e004013801981cf082ca478b2e5116a1839","tid":2173814,"uid":21545,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ab49325c54a35727c69b4d9dc8c64ddc612eeb64","tid":21738